  subtitleLines:
  - text: After retirement, I took my cat to the countryside,
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: feeling light and gay.
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: I watched it play on the grass,
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: every minute felt like a treasure to stay.
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: "we gave all to each other\u2019s side, "
    delayAfter: 6
  - text: "yet when it left, I couldn\u2019t walk away."
    delayAfter: 100
